<i>adverb</i>: 어제 [어제], 어저께 [어저께] <i>noun</i>: 어제 [어제], 어저께 [어저께] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>어제 [어제]</dt><br>
<dd>yesterday</dd><br>
<dd>오늘의 하루 전날에.</dd><br>
<dd>On the day before today.</dd><br>
<dt>어저께 [어저께]</dt><br>
<dd>yesterday</dd><br>
<dd>오늘의 하루 전날에.</dd><br>
<dd>On the day before today.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>어제 [어제]</dt><br>
<dd>1. yesterday</dd><br>
<dd>오늘의 하루 전날.</dd><br>
<dd>The day before the present day.</dd><br>
<dd>2. yesterday</dd><br>
<dd>지나간 때.</dd><br>
<dd>The time that has gone by.</dd><br>
<dt>어저께 [어저께]</dt><br>
<dd>yesterday</dd><br>
<dd>오늘의 하루 전날.</dd><br>
<dd>The day preceding today.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>